title: Patrick Miranda from Movements
itunes:title: Patrick Miranda from Movements
description:
Welcome to the Fall and dive into this fun discussion with Patrick Miranda from Movements. We talk about growing up in Orange County, the birth of MySpace discovery and being a hardcore kid. He was forthcoming and open about all of the questions I hit him with, which in my mind...makes a great episode. Enjoy!
